{"type":"text","timestamp":1775867079687,"sessionID":"ses_2861567eeffe7OxVP1P7gfHjxK","part":{"id":"prt_d79ed2731001zZe5XeCwlx5u1q","messageID":"msg_d79ed05fc001E2c72MnCsyLSZ5","sessionID":"ses_2861567eeffe7OxVP1P7gfHjxK","type":"text","text":"I see the root `design.md` is for AR-006. Based on the spec, I should write the design for AR-013 (Redis storage implementation) in the `changes/AR-013/design.md` file. Let me update that file:","time":{"start":1775867079684,"end":1775867079684}}}
