{"type":"text","timestamp":1775867206626,"sessionID":"ses_2861567eeffe7OxVP1P7gfHjxK","part":{"id":"prt_d79eef53c001ozQFf47riiGjFV","messageID":"msg_d79eee362001vz8cDfe2jWM0lf","sessionID":"ses_2861567eeffe7OxVP1P7gfHjxK","type":"text","text":"I've written the comprehensive design document for AR-013 (Redis Storage Implementation) at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/design.md`.\n\nThe design document includes:\n\n## Summary\n\n**AR-013: Redis Storage Implementation**\n- **Module**: `pkg/store`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: Medium\n\n### Key Sections Covered:\n\n1. **Architecture** - High-level design with interface-based abstraction supporting both Redis and Valkey backends\n\n2. **Data Structures**:\n   - `Store` interface with 8 methods (Ping, Get, Store, Update, Delete, ListExpired, ListInactive, UpdateActivity, Close)\n   - `redisStore` struct with Redis client and key prefixes\n   - Key patterns: `session:`, `session:expiry`, `session:last_activity`\n\n3. **API Contracts**:\n   - Key naming convention: `session:{sessionID}`\n   - ZSET score semantics for expiry and activity tracking\n\n4. **Method Implementations**:\n   - Detailed implementation for all 8 Store methods\n   - Pipeline operations for atomic updates\n   - Error handling patterns\n\n5. **Error Handling**:\n   - `ErrNotFound` sentinel error\n   - Error translation from Redis-specific errors\n\n6. **Configuration**:\n   - `STORE_TYPE` provider selection (redis/valkey)\n   - Environment variables for Redis and Valkey\n\n7. **Singleton Pattern** - Thread-safe initialization with `sync.Once`\n\n8. **Pipeline Operations Summary** - Atomic operations table\n\n9. **Testing Strategy** - Unit and integration test approaches\n\n10. **Dependencies** - go-redis/v9, klog/v2\n\n11. **File Structure** - Package files overview\n\nThe LSP errors detected are pre-existing issues in the `redis.go` and `valkey.go` implementation files and are not related to the design document I wrote.","time":{"start":1775867206624,"end":1775867206624}}}
